##  NOTES PENTING

### Format Waktu:
- ✅ Android kirim: `"08:00:00"` (HH:MM:SS)
- ✅ Laravel expect: `"08:00:00"` (HH:MM:SS)
- ✅ Database simpan: `08:00:00` (TIME)

### UUID:
- Laravel generate UUID otomatis di Model
- Android terima UUID sebagai String
- Mapping sudah benar di ScheduleApiModel

### User ID:
- Laravel ambil dari `$request->user()->id` (user yang login)
- Android tidak perlu kirim user_id (otomatis)

### Hari (Day):
- Validation: `Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday,Sunday`
- Harus exact match (capital first letter)

